    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Lifestyle Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Assistant Store Manager to strengthen our Jabalpur-based team.\n\nAbout Lifestyle Advisory Limited:\nLifestyle Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Lifestyle Advisory Limited!",
